      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>C Kaustubh</author>
      <guid>https://c-kaustubh.netlify.app/contact.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;contact&#34;&gt;Contact&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Email is the best way to reach me. I&#39;m generally responsive within a day.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Email&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:kaustubhc.1105@gmail.com&#34;&gt;kaustubhc.1105@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic&#34;&gt;github.com/snigenigmatic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;a href=&#34;https://linkedin.com/in/c-kaustubh&#34;&gt;linkedin.com/in/c-kaustubh&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I am actively looking for internship opportunities in Bengaluru and remote, primarily in ML, MLOps, systems, and backend engineering for Fall 2026. If something sounds relevant, please reach out.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>C Kaustubh</title>
      <link>https://c-kaustubh.netlify.app/index.html</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>C Kaustubh</author>
      <guid>https://c-kaustubh.netlify.app/index.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;home-hero&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;div class=&#34;home-hero-copy&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;p class=&#34;home-hero-meta&#34;&gt;CS undergraduate - systems, ML, infrastructure - Bengaluru&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;h1&gt;C Kaustubh&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;p class=&#34;home-intro&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;I build reliable distributed systems, ML pipelines, and performance-oriented developer tools with Rust, Go, Python, CUDA, and PyTorch.&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;div class=&#34;signal-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;div class=&#34;signal&#34; data-note=&#34;Systems&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;span&gt;Now&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;strong&gt;Teaching Assistant at PES University and Tech Lead at Shunya PESU.&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;div class=&#34;signal&#34; data-note=&#34;ML&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;span&gt;Research&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;strong&gt;RLHF/RLVR for ASR models, agentic memory, and video anomaly detection.&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;div class=&#34;signal&#34; data-note=&#34;Open Source&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;span&gt;Open Source&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;strong&gt;LanceDB, Firecracker, and core contributor to Vektori.&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;aside class=&#34;home-portrait&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;img src=&#34;/static/Kaustubh.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Portrait of C Kaustubh&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/aside&gt;&#xA;&lt;/section&gt;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;home-quick&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;article class=&#34;info-panel&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;h2&gt;Focus&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;p&gt;Distributed systems, ML systems, cloud-native infrastructure, and low-level performance.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;article class=&#34;info-panel&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;h2&gt;Proof&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;p&gt;Research intern at C-ISFCR, Deployfest 2026 runner-up, and multiple from-scratch systems projects.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;article class=&#34;info-panel&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;h2&gt;Open To&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;p&gt;Fall 2026 internships in ML, MLOps, systems, backend engineering, and applied AI R&amp;D.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;/section&gt;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;featured-project&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;h3&gt;Featured: qwen_cuda&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;From scratch implementation of a CUDA backend for the Qwen model family, optimizing memory usage and computational efficiency. Improved benchmark scores by ~3 tok/s.&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;div class=&#34;project-links&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/qwen_cuda&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;View repository&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;a href=&#34;/projects.html&#34;&gt;Browse all projects&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/section&gt;&#xA;&lt;nav class=&#34;page-actions&#34; aria-label=&#34;Primary links&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;a href=&#34;/about.html&#34;&gt;About&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;a href=&#34;/projects.html&#34;&gt;Projects&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;a href=&#34;/contact.html&#34;&gt;Contact&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;a href=&#34;/resume.html&#34;&gt;Resume&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Projects</title>
      <link>https://c-kaustubh.netlify.app/projects.html</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>C Kaustubh</author>
      <guid>https://c-kaustubh.netlify.app/projects.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;projects&#34;&gt;Projects&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Built for systems reliability, low-level performance, and applied ML. Full source at &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic&#34;&gt;github.com/snigenigmatic&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;project-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/qwen_cuda&#34; alt=&#34;qwen_cuda project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/qwen_cuda&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;qwen_cuda&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;From scratch implementation of a CUDA backend for the Qwen model, optimizing memory usage and computational efficiency. Improved benchmark scores by ~3 tok/s&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;CUDA · ML · Optimization · Performance&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/rust_cluster_simulator&#34; alt=&#34;cluster-simulator project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/rust_cluster_simulator&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;cluster-simulator&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;Implemented Kubernetes-style control-plane logic in safe Rust with scheduling, health checks, and leader-follower coordination.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;Rust · Distributed Systems · Control Plane · CI&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/redis-from-scratch&#34; alt=&#34;redis-from-scratch project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/redis-from-scratch&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;redis-from-scratch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;Built RESP3 compatibility with Pub-Sub and used it as a backing store for a REST API based Kafka clone.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;Go · RESP3 · In-Memory Store · Systems&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/sql-engine&#34; alt=&#34;sql-engine project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/sql-engine&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;sql-engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;An educational SQL database engine built from scratch in C++ to understand database internals. &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;C++ · Database Systems · Query Processing · Optimization&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/orderbook&#34; alt=&#34;orderbook project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/orderbook&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;orderbook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;Benchmarked matching engines to nanosecond-level latencies across x64 and ARM using C++20 and custom timing utilities.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;C++20 · High Performance · Low Latency · Benchmarking&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/YAK&#34; alt=&#34;YAK project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/YAK&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;YAK&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;Designed a Kafka-style event stream with replication, offsets, and leader-follower architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;Python · Distributed Systems · Pub-Sub · Replication&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/code-ronin&#34; alt=&#34;code-ronin project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/code-ronin&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;code-ronin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;Won Agentathon &#39;26 by turning debugging practice into an adversarial AI game loop.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;Python · AI Agents · Developer Education · Gamification&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/MediChain-FL&#34; alt=&#34;MediChain-FL project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/MediChain-FL&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;MediChain-FL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;Reached 93% pneumonia detection accuracy with federated training and no raw patient data exposure.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;Python · PyTorch · Flower · CKKS Encryption · Ethereum&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;project-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;project-media&#34; src=&#34;https://opengraph.githubassets.com/1/snigenigmatic/InsightInvest&#34; alt=&#34;InsightInvest project preview&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;project-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;project-title&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/snigenigmatic/InsightInvest&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;InsightInvest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-impact&#34;&gt;Automated multi-source company analysis and generated structured investment outlooks through an agentic workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;Python · LLM Agents · Finance Research · Structured Reports&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;/section&gt;&#xA;</description>
    </item>
